snippet.title: FFXIV Music! - Relaxing Song (Amh Araeng - Fields of Amber) Final Fantasy Soundtrack
snippet.description:
Super relaxing song that can be heard in Amh Araeng in Final Fantasy XIV!  This ethereal / jazz song recorded specifically in Fields of Amber region of Amh Araeng during gameplay.  Enjoy!
